{"slug":"oav-puri-results-2026-key-highlights","id":"oav-puri-results-2026-key-highlights","title":"OAV Puri Results 2026 Key Highlights","category":"Education","org":"Odisha","vacancies":"","lastDate":"","postDate":"2026-04-01","applyMode":"Online","location":"Odisha","shortInfo":"Odisha","sourceUrl":"https://puri.odisha.gov.in","education":[],"state":["Odisha"],"tags":["result","odisha","latest"],"detail":{"title":"OAV Puri Results 2026 Key Highlights","short_info":"OAV Puri Result 2026 released for Class 6, 7, 8 and 9 entrance/selection lists of OAV Astaranga, Brahmagiri, Delang, Gop, Kanasa, Krushnaprasad, Nimapara, Pipili, Purisadar, Satyabadi and Kakatpur schools on the official website - puri.odisha.gov.in on 31-03-2026. Check the direct PDF links here and know how to download the OAV Puri result.","sections":[{"heading":"","content":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"Odisha Adarsha Vidyalaya (OAV) Puri has announced the OAV Puri Result 2026 for admission/selection to Classes VI, VII, VIII and IX for various OAVs located in Astaranga, Brahmagiri, Delang, Gop, Kanasa, Krushnaprasad, Nimapara, Pipili, Purisadar, Satyabadi and Kakatpur under Puri district. OAV Puri Result 2026 has been released online on the official district website - puri.odisha.gov.in - in the form of separate PDF selection lists for each school and class."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Students and parents can check the OAV Puri selection list by opening the respective PDF for their OAV and class (for example, OAV Astaranga Class VI/VII/VIII, OAV Gop Class VI-IX etc.) and searching for the candidate’s name or roll number. After downloading the result PDF, they should carefully verify the candidate details, allotted school and class and follow the instructions given by the OAV/district office regarding document verification, admission dates and further formalities."}]},{"heading":"OAV Puri Results 2026 Key Highlights","content":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"The latest OAV Puri Result 2026 covers multiple Odisha Adarsha Vidyalayas in Puri district, providing class wise selection/merit lists for new admissions in Classes 6, 7, 8 and 9. These PDFs contain the names/roll numbers of selected candidates for OAVs at Astaranga, Brahmagiri, Delang, Gop, Kanasa, Krushnaprasad, Nimapara, Pipili, Purisadar, Satyabadi and Kakatpur, allowing families to quickly confirm admission status."},{"type":"table","headers":[],"rows":[["Authority"],["Result Year"],["Result Type"],["Schools Covered"],["Classes"],["Result Date"],["Official Website"],["Result/Notice Page"]]}]},{"heading":"OAV Puri Result 2026 Direct Link","content":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"The Puri district website hosts separate PDFs for each OAV and class, which act as the official selection/merit lists for OAV admissions. Students and parents can use the direct links below to open and download the relevant OAV Puri Result 2026 PDFs."},{"type":"important_links","links":[{"label":"OAV Astaranga Class VI Result 2026","url":"https://puri.odisha.gov.in/sites/default/files/2026-04/OAV%20ASTARANGA%20CLASS-VI.pdf"},{"label":"OAV Astaranga Class VII Result 2026","url":"https://puri.odisha.gov.in/sites/default/files/2026-04/OAV%20ASTARANGA%20CLASS-VII.pdf"},{"label":"OAV Astaranga Class VIII Result 2026","url":"https://puri.odisha.gov.in/sites/default/files/2026-04/OAV%20ASTARANGA%20CLASS-VIII.pdf"},{"label":"OAV Brahmagiri Class VI Result 2026","url":"https://puri.odisha.gov.in/sites/default/files/2026-04/OAV%20BRAHMAGIRI%20CLASS-VI.pdf"},{"label":"OAV Delang Class VI Result 2026","url":"https://puri.odisha.gov.in/sites/default/files/2026-04/OAV%20DELANG%20CLASS-VI.pdf"},{"label":"OAV Delang Class VII Result 2026","url":"https://puri.odisha.gov.in/sites/default/files/2026-04/OAV%20DELANG%20CLASS-VII.pdf"},{"label":"OAV Delang Class VIII Result 2026","url":"https://puri.odisha.gov.in/sites/default/files/2026-04/OAV%20DELANG%20CLASS-VIII.pdf"},{"label":"OAV Gop Class VI Result 2026","url":"https://puri.odisha.gov.in/sites/de